Description: I bought this guitar online 2 years ago and it just doesn't have the sound that I was looking for. Having said so, it has only been played a couple of times and is as close to new as I can imagine. I can't find any scratches or dings. I did wipe it down with some polish before I took these photos and it shows. It plays great and sounds very good. Will be packaged with a soft case, strap, new strings and batteries. Any questions, just ask. This guitar is very lightly used.
